text:
Love the place!

Great vibe and great service!

Made us feel welcomed and we also SING!

Thanks to ALL the singing uncles! They made our day! 🎼🎸🎤

😍🥰
Best retro bar of Singapore after madam Wong closed down.. Music is the best in Singapore foe those who likes retro
Retro or memories... Its hard to say... Because to me it feels like a good mix.
Great place to chill from 5 pm if you are alone and the lady bartender tried to chat with you
The Place where you can enjoy top retro music by DJ Kevin o hara
